JOB VIEWS:

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CRON JOB: TO SCHEDULE THE WORK.
CRON  SYNTAX: * * * * *

*	: MINUTES
*   : HOURS
*	: DATE
*	: MONTH
*   : DAY OF WEEK (SUN=0, MON=1, T=2 ---- S=6)


POLL SCM: It will trigger the build if source code is changed.

WEBHOOK: When dev chnages the code job will trigger immedieately.


